{"tid":334984,"cid":11,"subCid":0,"title":"有冇人以前睇過一套叫\"禽獸真面目\"？","createTime":"2017-07-25T08:22:44.000Z","updateTime":"2017-07-26T13:18:27.000Z","uid":92783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36af2cfe3934449601c8f4e18a0c09e524502825","tid":334984,"uid":92783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T08:22:44.000Z","msg":"唔記得亞視定明珠台播嘅<br />\n內容講d動物兇殘一面/襲擊人類<br />\n例如有個男人俾黑熊襲擊，已經奄奄一息，隻熊仲不停撚狗咁撚佢<br />\n又有馴獸師拖住隻老虎出場，隔離有個女人坐老虎隔離類似做訪問咁<br />\n中途隻老虎冇啦啦撲左個女人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 最後唔知有冇事<br />\n細個睇完之後發惡夢驚左好耐<br />\n十幾年前播過，但內容畫面就7/80年代<br />\n有冇巴打搵得返出黎？"},{"pid":"bc62fdf16ed26f6be186d7497c5c7517cd8217b1","tid":334984,"uid":92783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T09:15:42.000Z","msg":"冇人睇過？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d3398ca05298db9917cb660e73117a94d17466d3","tid":334984,"uid":92783,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:34:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11abd6131c1accf3f5c9f92399bdfa80c3b6e2bb","tid":334984,"uid":114097,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:38:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/203851_34f311b2202d776c63e4423c6c0f2a20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F07%2F25%2F203851_34f311b2202d776c63e4423c6c0f2a20.jpg&h=9fa405ad&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"2cae06f19eabf3e42dfedeb1ce9c6210c553e802","tid":334984,"uid":82532,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-07-25T12:39:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/07/25/203851_34f311b2202d776c63e4423c6c0f2a20.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%